= buildr4eclipse

* http://buildr4eclipse.rubyforge.org
* http://code.google.com/p/buildr4eclipse/

== DESCRIPTION:

Buildr is a ruby based build tool, this project is an extension to buildr to enable it to build eclipse based plugins. 

== FEATURES/PROBLEMS:

* This is pre-alpha quality!
* Bundles with the Eclipse compiler for Java.

== SYNOPSIS:

Use in your buildfile, require it like:
gem "buildr4eclipse"

== REQUIREMENTS:

* Buildr

== INSTALL:

* sudo gem install buildr4eclipse

